About the charity









        Right To Play UK
    

Right To Play is a global charity committed to helping children affected by poverty, disease and war through the simple concept of sport and play.

Through play, we help children to attend and stay in school, learn, and understand how to prevent common killers such as malaria, diarrhoea and HIV.
Charity Registration No. 1112404








